<paragraph id="78EED5BD6264B6686A20D7003A32D244" pageId="2" pageNumber="217">
<taxonomicName id="51DE5D4EEE055858F918237134559849" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Astochia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Astochia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="217" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Astochia</taxonomicName>
Becker, 1913: 538. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="6703CD676F30A66D21F8B5A98D0AFC79" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Astochia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Astochia metatarsata" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="217" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="metatarsata">Astochia metatarsata</taxonomicName>
